@startuml
title Get Park Reviews Activity

package "Front End" {
    actor Client
}

rectangle WebsiteParkPage <<component>> #LightBlue20-Reflected as BackEnd component> 
database ReviewsDB1 [Reviews] 

Client -> WebsiteParkPage : Visit park page\nWebsiteParkPage activates itself then sends request to activity controller which fetches data from DB via model layer before returning back through same path until finally presenting results on client side UI again completing full cycle of interaction between all involved components within system architecture design pattern used here namely MVC(Model View Controller).


@enduml
